data.description: Hi! I’m The Overlook of central Austin, your retreat in the heart of this fun city! I’m a modern, two story home just a short walk from some of Austin’s best restaurants, coffee shops, & bars. I’ve got 2 bedrooms with queen beds, a full bath upstairs, and a half bath downstairs. The open kitchen and living space make it easy to relax and feel at home! From kitchen essentials to fancy coffee to soft linens, I’ve got everything you need for a great stay! Well-behaved pets welcome w a fee 🐾
